original_title: Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 11: THE REVENGE
overview: "Lost & Found Vol. 11! THE REVENGE" is here to rip your dick off! Featuring psycho French splatter, Don’t Do Drugs puppets, Rick Moranis as Michael McDonald, a two headed gorilla, Alex Jones explaining “Twin Peaks: The Return”, music from Squeeze, Neil Young, T-Rex (twice!), Andy Kaufman, Yo La Tengo, The Cure and Dean Martin, Old Country Buffet training tips, a nazi getting his dick ripped off by an army of karate fighters, how to know if your kid is turning into a Satanist, “Sopranos” slaps, “Taxi Driver” filmed before a live studio audience, and an abundance of public access, instructional and religious video madness!
title: Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 11: THE REVENGE
